children.text: To move, press on the ground to move your character there.

children.name: text
children.text: Press on the green arrows to go to a new screen...

children.name: text
children.text: Press on a character to talk to them.

children.name: text
children.text: Some objects you can pick up by pressing on them.

children.name: text
children.text:
And lastly, you can always press on the Skwakpad icon to open it up.
There's a lot you can learn about Cyberspace and your quest from the Skwakpad!

Good luck!
